project_descr: The project aims to increase the number of local area development activities, promote local small and medium enterprises and provide vocational training to respond to the private sector’s needs.

outputs.output_descr: Outcome 1: Inclusive participatory processes in local area planning and decision making are institutionalized. Local communities are given a key role in influencing development priorities and in turn contribute to further stability and reconciliation
